<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="convinced-adj">convinced <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /kən'vɪnst/    美 /kən'vɪnst/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>确信的；坚信的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Sam nodded but he didn’t look convinced.
山姆点了点头，但似乎半信半疑。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I am <strong>convinced of</strong> her innocence.
我坚信她是无辜的。</p></div></div>